title: Brigitte Calls Me Baby wishes The Current a happy 20th anniversary

author: The Current
description:
Singer-songwriter Gigi Perez gives thanks to The Current and emphasizes the importance of public radio.

This year marks 20 years of listener-supported music discovery at The Current.
